high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the window, then hang a left and walk up to the oven.
Pick up the metal pan off of the front left burner of the stove.
Turn left and walk over to the door, then hang a left and walk up to the fridge.
Put the pan in the fridge for a couple seconds to get cold then take it back out and close the fridge.
Turn around and walk to the white table in the corner of the room.
Put the chilled pan on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled metal pan on a white table.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the oven
Grab the pan from the bottom left stove
Turn left and go to the fridge
Put the pan in the fridge and close the door. Then open the fridge and take it out
Turn around and stop at the white table
Put the pan on the table
anns.task_desc: Putting a pan on the white table

high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to stand in front of the stove.
Pick the pan from the bottom left of the stove up.
Go left and then left to face the fridge.
Put the pan in the fridge and shut the door and then open it and take the pan out again and shut the door.
Turn around and face the white table behind.
Put the pan on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan on a table.
